AccessDeniedException.documentation: This exception is thrown when the client doesn't have permission for the operation they requested.

AlreadyExistsException.documentation: This exception occurs when a user submits for an already existing script

EntityNotFoundException.documentation: This exception is thrown when the requested entity is not found in the server side.

InternalServiceException.documentation: This exception is thrown when a call fails due to internal error.

InvalidInputException.documentation: This exception is thrown when the format of the input is incorrect.

OperationTimeoutException.documentation: This exception occurs when the server throws a timeout

ValidationException.documentation: This exception occurs when the dag cannot be successfully validated
